|------|------|-------|---------|
| `pane.zig` | 174 | `[256:0]u8` | Shell path buffer |
| `event_loop.zig` | 791 | `[4096]u8` | PTY read buffer |
| `event_loop.zig` | 1267 | `[4096]u8` | Msgpack buffer |
| `event_loop.zig` | 1034 | `500` | Max cols/rows limit |
| `ipc.zig` | 233, 278 | `[4096]u8` | IPC buffers |
| `snapshot.zig` | 26 | `256` | Snappy compression threshold |
